content: I see there is a campaign event for the Harris speech on Facebook. Is the Walz rally in Lancaster and Pittsburg not being streamed? I have a small community that loves to watch all the stump events.

HI <@330179392284262411> the details of live campaign events have all been last-minute announcements (for security). Our discord doesn't have access to this info. You can oftne find out more from your local dems group.
I am confused, they don't announce Facebook streams early because of security? The Harris one is streamming and was anounced early. Why do they not stream Walz?
Sorry for confusion <@330179392284262411> . Details of live events are often last minute. The Facebook crew may not know if, or from where, there will be streaming
